  </sponsors>
  <source>Asociación para Evitar la Ceguera en México</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Intravitreal injection of Bevacizumab in patients with Neovascular Membranes secondary to
      intraocular inflammation. We injected a single injection of Bevacizumab (2.5 mg/0.1 ml) and
      evaluate visual acuity , Fluorescein angiogram and retinal thickness by Optical Coherence
      Tomography (OCT) in 4 patients with Vogt Koyanagi Harada disease, 1 patient with Serpiginous
      Choroidopathy and 1 patient with Multifocal Choroiditis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
